## SECTION 12 — CROSS-AI INTEROPERABILITY CHECKLIST

When testing with different models, ensure the AI can:

✓ Read PDFs, TXT, MD, JSON, or RTF
✓ Handle multistage prompts
✓ Distinguish summaries vs. analysis
✓ Execute reflexive self-correction
✓ Anchor claims in source text
✓ Perform concept linking
✓ Evaluate equations
✓ Detect contradictions
✓ Produce multi-pass reports
✓ Teach it back in simple language

This ensures cross-system replicability.

