## SECTION 14 — VALIDATION METRICS FOR CORRECTNESS

Any AI evaluating AURA must check:

- Internal coherence
- Equation traceability
- Step-wise reproducibility
- Triad constraint adherence
- Noise-bound behavior
- Emergent alignment
- Non-hallucinatory inference
- Compatibility with expectations of the files
- Logical consistency across passes

If a system passes all 9, its analysis is "Validated."

